quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  21,83,Ayub (alh-e-salam) ki uss halat ko yaad kero jabkay uss ney apney perwerdigar ko pukara kay mujhay yeh beemari lag gaee hai aur tu reham kerney walon say ziyada reham kerney wala hai
  21,84,To hum ney uss ki sunn li aur jo dukh unhen tha ussay door ker diya aur uss ko ehal-o-ayaal ata farmaye bulkay unn kay sath waisay hi aur apni khaas meharbaani say takay sachay bandon kay liye sabab naseehat ho
  21,85,Aur ismail (alh-e-salam) aur idris (alh-e-salam) aur zulkifl (alh-e-salam) yeh sab sabir log thay
  21,86,Hum ney unhen apni rehmat mein dakhil ker liya. Yeh sab log nek thay
  21,87,Machli walay (hazrat younus alh-e-salam) ko yaad kero! Jabkay woh gussay say chal diya aur khayal kiya kay hum ussay na pakar saken gay. Bil-aakhir woh andheron kay andar say pukar utha kay elahee teray siwa koi mabood nahi tu pak hai be-shak mein zalimon mein say tha
  21,88,To hum ney uss ki pukar sunn li aur ussay ghum say nijat dey di aur hum eman walon ko issi tarah bacha liya kertay hain
  21,89,Aur zakariya (alh-e-salam) ko yaad kero jab uss ney apney rab say dua ki aey meray perwerdigar! Mujhay tanah na chor tu sab say behtar waris hai
  21,90,Hum ney uss ki dua ko qabool farma ker ussay yahya (alh-e-salam) ata farmaya aur unn ki biwi ko unn kay liye durust ker diya. Yeh buzrug log nek kaamon ki taraf jaldi kiya kertay thay aur humen lalach tama aur darr khof say pukartay thay. Aur humaray samney aajzi kerney walay thay
  21,91,Aur woh pak daman bibi jis ney apni asmat ki hifazat ki hum ney uss kay andar apni rooh say phoonk di aur khud unhen aur unn kay larkay ko tamam jahan kay liye nishani bana diya
  21,92,Yeh tumhari ummat hai jo haqeeqat mein aik hi ummat hai aur mein tum sab ka perwerdigar hun pus tum meri hi ibadat kero
  21,93,Magar logon ney aapas mein apney deen mein firqa bandiyan ker len sab kay sab humari hi taraf lotney walay hain
  21,94,Phir jo bhi nek kaam keray aur woh momin (bhi) ho to uss ki kosish ki bey qadri nahi ki jayegi. Hum to iss kay likhney walay hain
  21,95,Aur jis basti ko hum ney halak ker diya uss per lazim hai kay wahan kay log palat ker nahi aayen gay
  21,96,Yahan tak kay yajooj aur majooj khol diye jayen gay aur woh her bulandi say dortay huye aayen gay
  21,97,Aur sacha wada qareeb aa lagay ga uss waqt kafirion ki nigahen phati ki phati reh jayen gi kay haye afsos! Hum iss haal say ghafil thay bulkay fil-waqey hum qusoor waar thay
  21,98,Tum aur Allah kay siwa jin jin ki tum ibadat kertay ho sab dozakh ka endhan bano gay tum sab dozakh mein janey walay ho
  21,99,Agar yeh (sachay) mabood hotay to jahannum mein dakhil na hotay aur sab kay sab ussi mein hamesha rehnay walay hain
  21,100,Aur woh wahan chilla reahey hongay aur wahan kuch bhi na sunn saken gay
  21,101,Albatta bey-shak jin kay liye humari taraf say neki pehlay hi ther chuki hai. Woh sab jahannum say door hi rakhay jayen gay
  21,102,Woh to dozakh ki aahat tak na sunen gay aur pani mann bhati cheezon mein hamesha rehney walay hongay
  21,103,Woh bari ghabrahat (bhi) unhen ghumgeen na ker sakay gi aur farishtay unhen hathon haath len gay kay yehi tumhara woh din hai jiss kay tum wada diye jatay rahey
  21,104,Jiss din hum aasman ko yun lapet len gay jaisay toomaar mein auraaq lapet diye jatay hain jaisay kay hum ney awwal dafa pedaeesh ki thi issi tarah doobara keren gay. Yeh humarayu zimmay wada hai aur hum issay zaroor ker kay (hi) rahen gay
  21,105,Hum zaboor mein pind-o-naseehat kay baad yeh likh chukay hain kay zamin kay waris meray nek banday (hi) hongay
  21,106,Ibadat guzaar bandon kay liye to iss mein aik bara payghaam hai
  21,107,Aur hum ney aap ko tamam jahan walon kay rehmat bana ker hi bheja hai
  21,108,Keh dijiye! Meray pass to pus wahee ki jati hai kay tum sab ka mabood aik hi hai to kiya tum bhi uss ki farmanbardaari kerney walay ho
  21,109,Phir agar yeh mun mor len to keh dijiye kay mein ney tumhen yaksan tor per khabardaar ker diya hai. Mujhay ilm nahi kay jiss ka wada tum say kiya jaraha hai woh qareeb hai ya door
  21,110,Albatta Allah Taalaa to khulli aur zahir baat ko bhi janta hai aur jo tum chupatay ho ussay bhi janta hai
  21,111,Mujhay iss ka bhi ilm nahi mumkin hai yeh tumhari aazmaeesh ho aur aik muqarrara waqt tak ka faeeda (phonchana) hai
  21,112,Khud nabi ney kaha aey rab! Insaf kay sath faisla farma aur humara rab bara meharbaan hai jiss say madad talab ki jati hai unn baaton per jo tum biyan kertay ho